author: jmduarte
body:
This adds the DeepDoubleB model V01 transformed to a constant GraphDef format, as in the DeepFlavour case. Two version of the DeepDoubleB model V01 (one with a mass sculpting penalty and one without) are available. Both expect a minimum candidate pT of 0.95 (as in the DeepFlavour model).

These model files will be used for an imminent pull request for the DeepDoubleB model in CMSSW.
title: add DeepDoubleB model V01 in GraphDef format
